title: CNN
video_name: Harris' poll numbers climb as she gains momentum
description:
According to a new CNN poll conducted by SSRS, Trump holds 49% support among registered voters nationwide to Harris’ 46%, a finding within the poll’s margin of sampling error. That’s a closer contest than earlier CNN polling this year had found on the matchup between Biden and Trump. Watch CNN's coverage.

title: CNN
video_name: Coconuts, brat, and Kamala Harris: What Does it Mean?
description:
Every presidential campaign eventually finds ways to take advantage of the cultural moment. Vice President Harris’s current moment in the viral sun happened as soon as she became the frontrunner of the Democratic ticket. How and why did it happen? Audie talks with two observers: researcher Nina Jankowicz (https://www.bloomsbury.com/us/how-to-be-a-woman-online-9781350267572/) , who studied online gendered abuse and disinformation against women in political life. And Deja Foxx﻿ (https://dejafoxx.com/) , who worked on Harris's 2019 campaign when she was just 19 years old, leading the digital team’s influencer and surrogate strategy.

description: Sen. Chuck Grassley (R-IA) released new video of investigators talking with local law enforcement on the roof where Thomas Crooks – the man who attempted to assassinate Donald Trump – was shot and killed. #CNN #News

title: CNN
video_name: Are Republican voters having doubts about Vance? Analyst breaks down the data
description:
CNN senior data reporter Harry Enten breaks down the numbers around JD Vance since his announcement as Donald Trump's vice presidential pick. CNN’s Danny Freeman asks Pennsylvania voters about their thoughts on JD Vance. #CNN #news

video_name: Whale breaches water and lands on boat in New Hampshire
